  m_Name: NickelNoumanDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  npcName: Nickel-And-Dime Nouman
  npcSprite: {fileID: -7527145504033472756, guid: 13c5bd9fa080d8a45a02886989dc863e, type: 3}
  dialogue:
  - '*picks nose*'
  - Hehe.
  - The name is Nickel-And-Dime Nouman. I love money, just like my daddy, the Merchant King.
  - '*sees 10-Yen bill in your pocket*'
  - MONEY! MONEY MONEY MONEY.
  - Is that for me??
  - 'No'
  - '*picks nose again*'
  - My dad says he's waiting for you inside.
  - "Everyone calls him the Merchant King Modi.\nI'm only allowed to let you in after you figure out his \"true name.\""
  - Whatever that means.
  - Oh, and apparently he has the packet you need to deliver.
  - So tell me, buddy. What's my dad's name?
  - That's right! My big daddy will see you now!
  - Wrong. That answer jingles like counterfeit copper.
  - Nope. Even my pocket lint knows better than that.
  - Embarrassing. Come back when your wallet grows a brain.
